    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect to replace the brake pads soon and address a minor slow leak in the power steering fluid. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable door dings and some fading on the clear coat on the hood. The interior is intact but would benefit from a deep clean, as there are some stains on the rear upholstery and the driver's side floor mat is worn through.",
