      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both mechanical precision and aesthetic appeal. It features a comprehensive service history and has undergone a thorough multi-point inspection to ensure continued reliability. This selection offers a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value, standing as a testament to diligent previous ownership and rigorous quality standards.",
