    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It still runs like a dream and is in really solid shape! The interior is super clean, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. It\u2019s perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town in style. You're going to love how it handles\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
