      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professional touch-up on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all original wood trim is free of cracks. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and power sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and there are no warning lights on the dash. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a folder of service receipts. This is a solid, honest example of a driver's car that has been cared for with an open checkbook.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
